    <item>
      <title>勒梅尔称法国将在不增加税收的情况下实现赤字目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/le-maire-says-france-to-meet-deficit-goal-without-tax-increases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔表示，尽管经济增长疲弱和税收收入令人失望，破坏了最初的计划，但政府将在不提高税收的情况下实现控制预算赤字的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/le-maire-says-france-to-meet-deficit-goal-without-tax-increases</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 12:51:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国通过32亿欧元法案减轻企业负担</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/germany-passes-3-2-billion-bill-to-ease-burden-on-companies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国议会上院通过了一项稀释后的法案，为企业提供 32 亿欧元（合 35 亿美元）的减税措施，结束了联合政府、联邦各州和主要反对党之间数月的争执。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/germany-passes-3-2-billion-bill-to-ease-burden-on-companies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 11:34:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京发言人称俄罗斯在乌克兰“处于战争状态”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/putin-s-spokesman-says-russia-is-in-a-state-of-war-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京的发言人表示，俄罗斯在乌克兰“处于战争状态”，而克里姆林宫通常将这次入侵描述为所谓的特别军事行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/putin-s-spokesman-says-russia-is-in-a-state-of-war-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 10:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
