      <title>波兰立法者预计对央行行长进行长期调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/polish-lawmaker-expects-lengthy-probe-of-central-bank-governor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰执政联盟正在准备对央行行长亚当·格拉平斯基(Adam Glapinski)进行旷日持久的调查，因为他的支持者（目前属于反对党）试图阻止可能导致行长下台的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/polish-lawmaker-expects-lengthy-probe-of-central-bank-governor</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 05:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
